      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "# **THOR Robot-Simulation Assistant**\n",
        "### Author: Levy Thiga Kariuki             \n",
        "\n",
        "\n",
        "This notebook presents an end-to-end intelligent assistant for a kitchen robot task in AI2-THOR: fetching a mug from a cupboard and placing it next to a microwave. The system integrates regression, classification, clustering, association rule mining, anomaly detection, and a capstone runtime policy.\n",
        "\n",
        "The regression target is `task_duration_sec`, and the classification target is `success`. These components are combined into a final decision-making loop that supports both normal execution and recovery behaviour."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "oeYSoKW3Pbqf"
      }
    },
    {
