    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "## 3.7 Robustness Check: Removing `avg_speed`"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "jH7doofkk7Zh"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "This robustness check is performed to assess how dependent the model is on `avg_speed`, which was identified as the dominant feature in the feature importance analysis. While `avg_speed` strongly predicts task duration, it may act as a proxy for execution time rather than a true causal driver.\n",
        "\n",
        "The goal of this experiment is to evaluate whether the model can still perform effectively using only environmental and interaction-based features (e.g., obstacles, clutter, grasp attempts). This helps determine whether the model is learning meaningful patterns or relying heavily on a single dominant variable.\n",
        "\n",
        "By removing `avg_speed`, we test the robustness and generalisability of the model under more constrained and realistic feature conditions."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "GhTlFBJ-wc64"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# Remove average speed\n",
        "features_no_speed = [\n",
        "    'path_len_m',\n",
        "    'obstacles_seen',\n",
        "    'grasp_attempts',\n",
        "    'doors_opened',\n",
        "    'collision_count',\n",
        "    'cupboard_open_init',\n",
        "    'clutter_level',\n",
        "    'distractors_level'\n",
        "]\n",
        "\n",
        "X_ns = df[features_no_speed]\n",
        "y = df['task_duration_sec']\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "OTW8GvoidaOj"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "X_train_ns, X_test_ns, y_train_ns, y_test_ns = train_test_split(\n",
        "    X_ns, y,\n",
        "    test_size=0.20,\n",
        "    random_state=42\n",
        ")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "SxZxR1qNdcxG"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "preprocessor_ns = ColumnTransformer(\n",
        "    transformers=[\n",
        "        (\"num\", StandardScaler(), features_no_speed)\n",
        "    ]\n",
        ")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "bJ3sYdrgdgzW"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#Random forest model\n",
        "rf_ns_pipeline = Pipeline(steps=[\n",
        "    (\"preprocessor\", preprocessor_ns),\n",
        "    (\"model\", RandomForestRegressor(\n",
        "        n_estimators=300,\n",
        "        random_state=42,\n",
        "        n_jobs=-1\n",
        "    ))\n",
        "])\n",
        "\n",
        "rf_ns_cv = cross_validate(\n",
        "    rf_ns_pipeline,\n",
        "    X_train_ns,\n",
        "    y_train_ns,\n",
        "    cv=KFold(n_splits=5, shuffle=True, random_state=42),\n",
        "    scoring=('neg_mean_absolute_error','neg_mean_squared_error','r2')\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "mae_ns = -rf_ns_cv[\"test_neg_mean_absolute_error\"]\n",
        "mse_ns = -rf_ns_cv[\"test_neg_mean_squared_error\"]\n",
        "r2_ns  =  rf_ns_cv[\"test_r2\"]\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"CV MAE:\", mae_ns.mean())\n",
        "print(\"CV MSE:\", mse_ns.mean())\n",
        "print(\"CV R2:\", r2_ns.mean())\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "OyM7DBuJdjS7",
        "outputId": "839655a5-c634-4e2b-c3da-9e42417b6413"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "CV MAE: 1.2292337289051798\n",
            "CV MSE: 6.167240028331328\n",
            "CV R2: 0.4980787177862383\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "#Linear regression model\n",
        "rf_ns_pipeline.fit(X_train_ns, y_train_ns)\n",
        "y_pred_ns = rf_ns_pipeline.predict(X_test_ns)\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Test MAE:\", mean_absolute_error(y_test_ns, y_pred_ns))\n",
        "print(\"Test MSE:\", mean_squared_error(y_test_ns, y_pred_ns))\n",
        "print(\"Test R2:\", r2_score(y_test_ns, y_pred_ns))\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "GKV-J5cDdoEh",
        "outputId": "68091f93-e86f-49e5-bd1e-4bc517f86eb4"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "Test MAE: 1.4733843410729877\n",
            "Test MSE: 11.803150029169542\n",
            "Test R2: 0.33323749796961577\n"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
